    <Unit id="thrower_3" category="unitcategory_artillery">
      <Name>Stone Thrower</Name>
      <Name lang="de_DE">Steinschleuderer</Name>
      <Description lang="de_DE">
        <p>Der Steinschleuderer ist ein sehr durchschlagkräftiger Fernkämpfer.</p> 
      </Description>
      <Description lang="en_US">
        <p>You can throw bigger stones even further if you use a catapult. Stone throwers often hit unsuspecting warriors in the second row, leading to a much higher number of overall casualties that are either suffered or celebrated, depending on which side of the battle you happen to be. Which isn't always obvious.</p>
      </Description>
      <Flavour lang="en_US">
        <p>The stone thowers have a simple motto - the further you can throw the stone, the better!</p>
      </Flavour>
      <Flavour lang="de_DE">
        <p>Das Motto der Steinschleuderer: 'Je weiter der Stein geworfen wird, desto besser!'</p>
      </Flavour>
